OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779962735
OL,3,CPolice met with 'violence and
OL,4,Chostility' in Bournemouth beach
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FDorset Police says its officers were
OL,8,Fmet with "violence and hostility" as
OL,9,Fthey responded to "unacceptable
OL,10,Fdisorder" on Bournemouth beach.
OL,12,FThe force said it arrested three
OL,13,Fpeople on Tuesday evening after a
OL,14,Ffight broke out near Bournemouth Pier.
OL,16,FOfficers also dispersed a "large
OL,17,Fnumber of people" in the resulting
OL,18,Fdisorder, which led to glass bottles
OL,19,Fand objects being thrown.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779962735
OL,3,CPolice met with 'violence and
OL,4,Chostility' in Bournemouth beach
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FThose arrested included a 22-year-old
OL,8,Fman, from London, on suspicion of
OL,9,Fpossession of an offensive weapon in a
OL,10,Fpublic place.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FTwo 17-year-old boys were also
OL,18,Fdetained. One of the teenagers, from
OL,19,FSouthampton, was arrested on suspicion
OL,20,Fof affray and assault.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779962735
OL,3,CPolice met with 'violence and
OL,4,Chostility' in Bournemouth beach
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FThe other, from Portsmouth, was
OL,8,Farrested on suspicion of affray.
OL,10,FChief Superintendent Julie Howe,
OL,11,FBournemouth, Christchurch and Poole
OL,12,F(BCP) Local Policing Commander, said:
OL,13,F"The levels of violence and disorder
OL,14,Fwe saw last night on the beach were
OL,15,Fabsolutely unacceptable and not
OL,16,Fsomething we will tolerate here in
OL,17,FDorset.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779962735
OL,3,CPolice met with 'violence and
OL,4,Chostility' in Bournemouth beach
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,F"Over the bank holiday weekend we had
OL,8,Fmany families enjoying our beaches
OL,9,Frespectfully and we would like to
OL,10,Fthank all law-abiding visitors, but
OL,11,Fyesterday there were groups of young
OL,12,Fpeople who had travelled from out of
OL,13,Fthe county and were intent on causing
OL,14,Fdisorder.
OL,16,F"We have commenced a robust
OL,17,Finvestigation into the events of last
OL,18,Fnight and will be working to make sure
OL,19,Fanyone involved is held accountable
OL,20,Ffor their behaviour.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779962735
OL,3,CPolice met with 'violence and
OL,4,Chostility' in Bournemouth beach
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,F"I want to praise the officers who
OL,8,Fwere involved for their professional
OL,9,Fand courageous actions.
OL,11,F"The swift response quickly de-
OL,12,Fescalated the situation and prevented
OL,13,Fany further large-scale disorder.
OL,15,F"Not only were they trying to prevent
OL,16,Fthe situation from escalating, they
OL,17,Fwere also responding to critical
OL,18,Fmedical emergencies on the beach,
OL,19,Fwhich included giving CPR to a woman
OL,20,Fand helping provide support to the
OL,21,Fambulance service.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779962735
OL,3,CPolice met with 'violence and
OL,4,Chostility' in Bournemouth beach
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,F"This type of disorder takes officers
OL,8,Faway from dealing with what matters
OL,9,Fmost, protecting the public."
OL,11,FChief Superintendent Howe confirmed
OL,12,Fthat no officers were seriously
OL,13,Finjured in the disorder.
OL,15,FShe also dismissed a video on social
OL,16,Fmedia, which alleged that someone had
OL,17,Fbeen stabbed, saying this is
OL,18,F"incorrect and we are not aware of
OL,19,Fanyone sustaining any stab wounds or
OL,20,Fserious injuries".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779962735
OL,3,CPolice met with 'violence and
OL,4,Chostility' in Bournemouth beach
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FBCP Council Leader Millie Earl praised
OL,8,Fthe "swift response" of the police,
OL,9,Fadding the two agencies will work
OL,10,Fclosely together to ensure Bournemouth
OL,11,F"remains safe for the overwhelming
OL,12,Fmajority who do act responsibly".
OL,14,FThe disorder in Bournemouth comes
OL,15,Fafter similar incidents took place in
OL,16,FKent and Sussex over the bank holiday
OL,17,Fweekend.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
