OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779962735
OL,3,CPolice met with 'violence and
OL,4,Chostility' in Bournemouth beach
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FKent Police arrested six people as
OL,8,Fpart of an antisocial behaviour
OL,9,Fcrackdown, while a teenager was
OL,10,Fstabbed after reports of "people
OL,11,Ffighting" in Brighton.
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/8
